city: Enter the city name where the depot is located.(Example: Silverwater)
state: Enter the State name the depot is located in.(Example: NSW)
country: Enter the country where the depot is located.(Example: Australia)
region: Enter the region where the depot is located.  The regions are APAC EMEA or US.(Example: APAC)
hub: Enter 1 if the given depot is a hub. 0 otherwise.(Example: 1)
partner: Enter the name of the partner that is managing the depot.(Example: Choice Logistics)
partner_warehouse_code: Enter the partner warehouse code if one is available. Otherwise enter NULL.(Example: SYD)
contact: Enter the contact phone number of the Depot.(Example: +61 2 8756 3977)
lat: Enter the latitude where the Depot is located.(Example: -33.83641)
long: Enter the longitude of the depot location.(Example: 151.0334369)
